1
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 8=
(Danger Is Everywhere)

3
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,159
Something urgent came up at the company.

4
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,319
I need to go handle it.

5
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:28,040
You did nothing all day

6
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,319
and went out fooling around again.

7
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,319
Tell me, what part of you

8
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:34,040
behaves like a proper daughter-in-law?

9
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,599
Didn't you ask me to organize
the dressing room?

10
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,159
I finished organizing before I went out.

11
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,159
If you don't believe me, ask Xiaoling.

12
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:42,000
Madam Gu cleaned it thoroughly.

13
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,840
Since you're so capable,

14
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,680
for tomorrow's family banquet,

15
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,400
you help at the kitchen early.

16
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,719
Sure.

17
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,239
I can show off my skills.

18
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,640
For tomorrow's meal,

19
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,719
leave her to do the cooking alone.

20
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,359
Yes, Madam He.

21
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,079
Are you sure
the one lying in the hospital

22
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,799
is an employee of our factory?

23
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:02,959
Yes, Mr. He.

24
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,040
His name is Tian Gang.

25
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,000
He used to be a quality inspector
at our factory.

26
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,959
Because of his misconducts,

27
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,400
he was fired earlier this year.

28
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:12,000
Then why was he showing up
with Gu Qingmei?

29
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,280
We found out

30
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,080
that he had been posting

31
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,919
slanderous comments about us online

32
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:19,439
and had contact with Mrs. He.

33
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,960
There seemed to be some kind of deals.

34
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:24,080
What does she want?

35
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,319
Send someone to keep an eye on him

36
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,319
and find out their deal to report me.

37
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,400
Go.

38
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,199
Mr. He,

39
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:45,840
if you don't pay back the money,

40
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:49,120
don't blame me
for visiting your family later.

41
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:50,919
I told you, give me a few more days.

42
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:55,560
Enough!

43
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:57,479
One final week!

44
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,120
Got it.

45
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:07,280
Let's go.

46
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,719
How much are you still in debt?

47
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:18,159
Not much. I am almost there.

48
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,800
Your wife is the only daughter
of the Xu family,

49
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,800
surely she can help you pay this amount.

50
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,599
Dear, you are back.

51
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,840
Dear.

52
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:46,240
What is wrong?

53
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:50,159
I invested in a new energy project.

54
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,319
Although it is going smoothly,

55
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:54,960
I am having some cash flow issues.

56
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,120
You invested it yourself?

57
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,439
Does Dad know?

58
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,599
Of course not.

59
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,560
I want to prove myself first.

60
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,520
Otherwise, how could Dad ever trust me

61
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,199
with Shengda Group someday?

62
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,680
Dear,

63
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,240
can you

64
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,800
help me cover the funding gap first?

65
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:16,480
My money is managed
by my father's company.

66
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,399
He doesn't let me invest recklessly.

67
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,920
It is not an investment.

68
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,079
You just lend me the money
to get through this.

69
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,800
I'll pay you back
as soon as the project pays off.

70
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,800
Dear, you know,

71
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,879
in our family,

72
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,480
my brother has always been the favorite.

73
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,319
I've always been overlooked.

74
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:34,639
I also want to prove myself.

75
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,600
Please, dear.

76
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,000
Dear.

77
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,040
Please?

78
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:43,199
How much do you want?

79
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:44,839
Thirty million.

80
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:45,920
That much?

81
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,800
I only have twenty million on hand.

82
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,720
Twenty million works too.

83
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,839
I will figure out the rest myself.

84
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:55,959
Alright.

85
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,959
I will have the finance department
transfer it to you tomorrow.

86
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,639
Dear, I love you!

87
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,079
You are my treasure!

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,600
You are so good to me!

89
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,480
They've come after her more than once.

90
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,720
This drive must contain
some serious evidence.

91
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,160
TAF990.

92
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:21,600
It looks like some kind of chemical.

93
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,879
It's not listed
on the raw material sheet.

94
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:28,040
Boss.

95
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,519
The fish bit.

96
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,800
It is time to reel it in.

97
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:34,800
Wait.

98
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,800
Don't forget to give Second Young Master

99
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,240
a special surprise.

100
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,040
Understood.

101
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,560
What are you doing?

102
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,480
There is no mole on your chest.

103
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:59,399
You are not Gu Qingmei.

104
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:00,839
What's it to you

105
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,040
who I really am?

106
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,360
I can keep this secret for you,

107
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,439
as long as you cooperate with me

108
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,279
and give me ten million.

109
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,399
How are you going to expose me?

110
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,319
By saying you took a photo
of your sister-in-law?

111
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:17,439
And how do you even know about
the mole on my chest?

112
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,600
You...

113
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,720
You think I wouldn't dare?

114
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,079
If I don't get what I want,

115
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:21,920
neither will you!

116
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,000
Jinchuan?

117
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,399
Jinchen, this woman is not...

118
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,519
Dear!

119
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,920
He came to my dressing room
and took photos of me.

120
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,399
He even tried to blackmail me
for ten million!

121
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,839
You wretched woman!

122
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,439
What are you doing? Stay calm.

123
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,519
Yeah.

124
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:38,879
Tell us now.

125
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,720
Why were you hiding in the dressing room
taking photos of me

126
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:43,439
and blackmailing me for ten million?

127
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,560
Ten million?

128
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,519
You took photos
and blackmailed your sister-in-law?

129
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:51,839
I am sorry.

130
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,439
I am drunk.

131
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:54,360
I...

132
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,600
went into the wrong room.

133
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,600
I thought it was Niannian.

134
00:06:57,199 --> 00:06:58,000
Just joking.

135
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,360
Is that something to joke about?

136
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:01,199
All you do is fool around every day.

137
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,399
Cut back on the drinking!

138
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,040
Get out!

139
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,199
Alright.

140
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,240
Are you alright?

141
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,120
I am fine.

142
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,560
It is just that this family

143
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,959
is really not safe.

144
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,639
(An imposter.)

145
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,759
(I have plenty of ways
to prove your identity.)

146
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,399
I want to do a paternity test.

147
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,639
Thank you.

148
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:56,720
Everyone,

149
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,959
this is the family banquet
I have prepared for you.

150
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:01,199
Please enjoy.

151
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:08,560
Rice bowl?

152
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:12,720
Do you know who we are?

153
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,319
And you are serving us this?

154
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,120
Exactly.

155
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:18,000
Qingmei is really down to earth.

156
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:18,879
Anyone would think

157
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,879
our family was going broke.

158
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:24,360
Are you trying to embarrass our family?

159
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:26,560
Do you even care
about our family's reputation?

160
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,200
(Are you insane?)

161
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:37,840
(Yes!)

162
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,840
(I am insane!)

163
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,639
(Wealthy lady of high society?)

164
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,840
(Reputation?)

165
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:42,879
(I am done playing!)

166
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,480
(You...)

167
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,240
(You what?)

168
00:08:44,919 --> 00:08:46,559
(Playing a high-society lady every day.)

169
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,200
(Look at how you usually act.)

170
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,440
(You are just a shrew!)

171
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:50,879
(And you.)

172
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:52,440
(You have never earned a penny,)

173
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,879
(and yet you are criticizing others.)

174
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,320
(How dare you speak to my mother
like that?)

175
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,120
(Do you still want a place...)

176
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:56,759
(Shut up!)

177
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:58,279
(You think with your lower half,)

178
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,399
(and you are acting
all high and mighty here?)

179
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,039
(Gu Qingmei, you...)

180
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,039
(Have you lost your mind?)

181
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,279
(So you can speak.)

182
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,039
(All these years,)

183
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,440
(I've suffered so much in this family,)

184
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,000
(and you were not mute after all!)

185
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,720
Now get rid of this garbage.

186
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:21,879
Garbage?

187
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,919
How is a rice bowl garbage?

188
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:24,720
What,

189
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,960
rich people can't eat rice bowls?

190
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:30,399
I remember Dad once said,

191
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:32,279
even if we have become rich,

192
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,559
we should never forget our roots

193
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,960
or waste anything.

194
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,720
Am I right, Dad?

195
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:38,480
That's true.

196
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,679
Very good.

197
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,720
Qingmei did the right thing.

198
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:46,960
I absolutely hate wasting food.

199
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:49,679
Eat up!

200
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,399
With this quality,

201
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,159
even the dogs would not eat it!

202
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,120
An'an, slow down.

203
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,080
This is delicious.

204
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,039
I want more!

205
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:18,080
Qingmei,

206
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:20,440
you are really skilled at cooking.

207
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,600
This flavor

208
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,279
is even better than
the Michelin restaurants.

209
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,080
Thank you for the compliment.

210
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,480
This is just home cooking.

211
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:29,759
A family banquet

212
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,519
should feel like home.

213
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,039
Hello.

214
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,559
Alright, I will be right there.

215
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,399
I am sorry,

216
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:45,519
it's an urgent company matter,

217
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,399
I have to go.

218
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,799
Since it is company business,

219
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:51,159
let me go with you.

220
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:52,320
Alright.

221
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,240
Alright.

222
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:54,440
Shaoze...

223
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,360
I am sorry, everyone,

224
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:56,799
I have to excuse myself.

225
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,000
Look at your wonderful daughter-in-law.

226
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,960
She has no manners at all.

227
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,720
She doesn't respect me at all.

228
00:11:08,759 --> 00:11:09,679
Company matters

229
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,559
always come before a meal.

230
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,279
From now on,

231
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,720
I don't want to hear that again.

232
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,000
Mom.

233
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,519
I also hope that from now on,

234
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,320
you will not be so harsh with Qingmei.

235
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:28,519
She is your daughter-in-law,
not your enemy.

236
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,200
Go on, leave!

237
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:36,559
You and your father

238
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,879
are completely bewitched
by Gu Qingmei and her mother.

239
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:13,799
Mom.

240
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,919
Don't you think Gu Qingmei
has been acting strange?

241
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,240
What do you mean?

242
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:22,440
Ever since her accident,

243
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,279
it's like she's completely different.

244
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,840
After losing one's memory,

245
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,200
can personality change drastically?

246
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,519
What if

247
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,480
she's possessed?

248
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,919
You're right, Mom.

249
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,639
She must have been possessed!

250
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,000
Doctor,

251
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,080
with his condition,

252
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,480
when will he be able to speak again?

253
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,840
We are not sure at this point.

254
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,440
It depends on his recovery progress.

255
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:58,360
Keep watching him.

256
00:12:58,879 --> 00:12:59,679
I need to know

257
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,639
the relationship

258
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,000
between Gu Qingmei and Tian Gang.

259
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:08,440
Dad.

260
00:13:11,519 --> 00:13:12,120
Jinchen,

261
00:13:12,799 --> 00:13:13,759
have you and Qingmei

262
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,080
been having any problems lately?

263
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,120
No.

264
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:19,360
There is no problem between us.

265
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:22,559
Qingmei has changed a lot recently,

266
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,120
but

267
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,320
I don't want any problems

268
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,360
in your marriage.

269
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,000
Don't worry!

270
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:31,159
Although I neglected her before,

271
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,480
I am now trying to get to know her more

272
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,000
and give her more care.

273
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,360
Good.

274
00:13:37,519 --> 00:13:38,559
You know your younger brother

275
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,320
can't lead the family business.

276
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:43,320
So the family future falls on you.

277
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,879
But the most important thing right now

278
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,240
is to secure the Gu family.

279
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:50,799
I understand, Dad.

280
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:24,300
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

281
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:29,140
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

282
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:33,700
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

283
00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:38,620
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

284
00:14:38,620 --> 00:14:42,420
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

285
00:14:42,420 --> 00:14:47,220
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

286
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:50,060
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

287
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:52,740
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

288
00:14:53,100 --> 00:14:58,660
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

289
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:05,860
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

290
00:15:06,140 --> 00:15:10,820
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

291
00:15:10,980 --> 00:15:17,780
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

292
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:24,900
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

293
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:29,580
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

294
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:32,940
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

295
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:39,860
♪Right as I confess my love♪
